  "text": "The simulation results are plotted in Figure 1(a) , where the number of simulation runs on ER random-graph network model is 50, therefore totally 50 network realizations were generated by ER algorithm, and a total of 2500 × 50 subgraph centralities were plotted altogether in the same figure (they are not the averages of the subgraph centralities of the 50 simulations). Figure 1(b) shows the averages of the subgraph centralities of the ER model plotted in Figure 1 (a). To quantify the variability of the subgraph centralities, the relative deviations defined by [CITATION_1] were calculated and are plotted in Figure 2 . The ER algorithm was run with = 2500 and = 0.08.",
